      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=mjcxfbje7d]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mjcxfbje7d]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=x0lsco3flb]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=x0lsco3flb]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=obztez16tm]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=obztez16tm]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=pxk4ei0jow]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=pxk4ei0jow]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=bug4f8p6ws]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=bug4f8p6ws]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=n9u0e5vlp9]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=n9u0e5vlp9]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"MainHeader_header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/MainHeader_header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762158537630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=327\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145921/MainHeader_header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762158537630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"828\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"640352257\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"MainHeader_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145921\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"35\" data-media-id=\"56ca9863-1a78-47fc-9179-c055fea35101\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/MainHeader_header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762158537630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=654 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/MainHeader_header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762158537630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=327 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"LearningPaths-RenderManLearningPaths\"><span data-colorid=\"pxk4ei0jow\">RenderMan Learning Paths</span></h1><p>Whether you&rsquo;re a 3D artist new to RenderMan, a creative who&rsquo;s currently trying to enhance your skills, or a long-time industry veteran, these learning paths provide something for everyone.</p><p>Select a learning path and embark on an educational and creative journey!</p><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/599163154/Shading+Path\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599163154\" data-linked-resource-version=\"43\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"shading_learingPath.jpg\" width=\"565\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/shading_learingPath.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759727256509&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=238\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145921/shading_learingPath.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759727256509&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"238\" data-width=\"565\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"620396876\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shading_learingPath.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145921\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"35\" data-media-id=\"426112ec-64ea-4107-839e-4c4e505cc677\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/shading_learingPath.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759727256509&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=238 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/shading_learingPath.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759727256509&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=238 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"LearningPaths-Shading\"><span data-colorid=\"mjcxfbje7d\">Shading</span></h1><p>Take this path if you want to elevate your shaders, texturing &amp; lookdev.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/598901006/Lighting+Path\" data-linked-resource-id=\"598901006\" data-linked-resource-version=\"39\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"lighting_learingPath.jpg\" width=\"565\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/lighting_learingPath.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759759600328&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=238\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145921/lighting_learingPath.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759759600328&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"238\" data-width=\"565\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"620462395\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lighting_learingPath.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145921\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"35\" data-media-id=\"6fcc3b2c-5ba9-463f-86d6-37e78e8f0f7d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/lighting_learingPath.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759759600328&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=238 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/lighting_learingPath.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759759600328&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=238 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"LearningPaths-Lighting\"><span data-colorid=\"obztez16tm\">Lighting</span></h1><p>RenderMan features a complete set of physical analytic lights.  This path gets you started with lights and lighting.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"camera_learingPath_comingSoon.jpg\" width=\"623\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/camera_learingPath_comingSoon.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1762155611484&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145921/camera_learingPath_comingSoon.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1762155611484&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"636944395\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"camera_learingPath_comingSoon.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145921\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"35\" data-media-id=\"bd1e95c2-5a31-4bd9-95f7-1af5bdcda2a6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/camera_learingPath_comingSoon.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1762155611484&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1246&amp;height=524 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/camera_learingPath_comingSoon.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1762155611484&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"LearningPaths-Camera\"><span data-colorid=\"bug4f8p6ws\">Camera</span></h1><p>Add character, feeling, and depth to your camera with this learning path.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"vfx_learingPath_comingsoon.jpg\" width=\"623\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/vfx_learingPath_comingsoon.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1762155648411&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145921/vfx_learingPath_comingsoon.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1762155648411&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"636551200\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"vfx_learingPath_comingsoon.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145921\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"35\" data-media-id=\"4b801c1f-b568-4f11-a7c5-5b54855382e9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/vfx_learingPath_comingsoon.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1762155648411&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1246&amp;height=524 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/vfx_learingPath_comingsoon.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1762155648411&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"LearningPaths-VFX\"><span data-colorid=\"x0lsco3flb\">VFX</span></h1><p>For those into Visual Effects, this path is for you!</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/598901015/Rendering+Path\" data-linked-resource-id=\"598901015\" data-linked-resource-version=\"35\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"rendering_learingPath.jpg\" width=\"623\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/rendering_learingPath.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759765756713&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/600145921/rendering_learingPath.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759765756713&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"620495224\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rendering_learingPath.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"600145921\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"35\" data-media-id=\"21ff408e-1aaa-416c-8716-178f8ff9d48c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/rendering_learingPath.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759765756713&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1246&amp;height=524 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/rendering_learingPath.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759765756713&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"LearningPaths-Rendering\"><span data-colorid=\"n9u0e5vlp9\">Rendering</span></h1><p>This learning path will help you along your journey to becoming a Rendering Rockstar!</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/600145921/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1